<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="scroll-smooth" lang="it">

<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>

<body class="bg-background-light text-slate-800 font-sans transition-colors duration-300">
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 text-slate-100 dark:text-slate-900 bg-grid-pattern opacity-50 -z-10"></div>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">
            <span class="text-primary">Organizzazione</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Crediamo che l'efficienza non nasca da strutture complesse, ma da una comunicazione aperta e continua.
            Per noi è fondamentale che le informazioni circolino liberamente, in modo trasversale, senza barriere
            legate a ruoli, competenze o aree operative.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Nessun Compartimento Stagno -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div>
            <span
              class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
              Il nostro approccio
            </span>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
              Nessun compartimento stagno
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Nel nostro modo di lavorare non esistono barriere: ognuno porta competenze solide nel proprio ambito,
              ma con una <strong class="text-slate-800 dark:text-white">visione d'insieme condivisa</strong>.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl">
                <div
                  class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">code</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Chi sviluppa</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Conosce i sistemi e l'infrastruttura</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl">
                <div
                  class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">dns</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Chi lavora sull'infrastruttura</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Comprende il prodotto e il business</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl">
                <div
                  class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">handshake</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Chi segue la parte commerciale</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Ha familiarità con gli aspetti tecnici</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="aspect-square rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
              <img alt="Team che collabora in modo trasversale" class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?w=1200&q=80&fm=jpg&fit=crop" />
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Crescita e Formazione -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/30">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span
            class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
            Investiamo nelle persone
          </span>
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
            Crescita e Formazione
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Ogni collaboratore ha un percorso di sviluppo definito e monitorato, supportato da formazione continua.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Junior -->
          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 text-3xl">school</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Figure Junior</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Percorso di crescita strutturato</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5">check_circle</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Affiancamento a professionisti esperti</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5">check_circle</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Mentorship personalizzata</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5">check_circle</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Velocità di crescita basata su impegno e capacità</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Senior -->
          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">workspace_premium</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Figure Senior</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Formazione continua avanzata</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5">check_circle</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Formazione dedicata ogni anno</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5">check_circle</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Corsi, seminari e conferenze di settore</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg mt-0.5">check_circle</span>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Ampliamento e rafforzamento competenze</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Aree di formazione -->
        <div class="mt-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <h3 class="text-center font-bold text-lg mb-6 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Le nostre aree di formazione</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <!-- Metodologiche -->
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">sync_alt</span> Agile
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">task_alt</span> Project Management
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">verified</span> Certificazioni
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">groups</span> Gestione Team
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">cloud_queue</span> Cloud &amp; Infrastruttura
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">code</span> Sviluppo Software
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">security</span> Cyber Security
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">analytics</span> Data &amp; AI
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">integration_instructions</span> System Integration
            </span>
            <span class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm align-middle mr-1">terminal</span> DevOps &amp; Sysadmin
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Knowledge Days -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-primary text-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 border-8 border-white rounded-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white rounded-full translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 mb-12">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl">calendar_month</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-3">Knowledge Days</h2>
              <p class="text-white/80 text-lg">
                Due giornate all’anno dedicate alla crescita delle nostre persone.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/20">
            <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Crediamo che la vera efficienza nasca dalla condivisione, non dalla complessità. Per questo abbiamo istituito i Knowledge Days: due appuntamenti annuali, riconosciuti a livello aziendale, interamente dedicati alla formazione e allo scambio di competenze tra colleghi e con professionisti esterni.
Sono momenti pensati per fermarsi, uscire dalla routine operativa e investire tempo nella conoscenza: si approfondiscono temi specifici, si condividono esperienze concrete e si discutono approcci, strumenti e pratiche di lavoro.
Un’occasione per valorizzare ciò che funziona, imparare dagli errori e costruire insieme una cultura aziendale basata su apprendimento continuo, confronto e crescita condivisa.
            </p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">thumb_up</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold">Best Practices</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Le esperienze che hanno generato valore.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined">lightbulb</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-bold">Lessons Learned</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Gli insegnamenti che ci aiutano a migliorare.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>
